  <summary date="2021-11-23T18:55:37Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Task Force on the Impact of the Affordable Housing Crisis Act of 2021

This bill establishes the Task Force on the Impact of the Affordable Housing Crisis and requires the task force to make recommendations on how to use affordable housing to improve the effectiveness of federal programs and improve life outcomes.</summary>
